{"tid":2190552,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新疆絕育乃「自願」　中國駁斥德國研究人員對強制絕育的批評","createTime":"2020-09-05T18:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T08:54:04.000Z","uid":261647,"like":7,"dislike":120,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"a8dab208ea5e8d4522c3529eedec4f24f9ea384f","tid":2190552,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:25:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/knockofftranslation/photos/a.107312867772482/109047527599016/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fknockofftranslation%2Fphotos%2Fa.107312867772482%2F109047527599016%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=8a0191f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/knockofftranslation/photos/a.107312867772482/109047527599016/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A78fabn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA78fabn.jpg&h=d097214c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【新疆絕育乃「自願」 中國駁斥德國研究人員對強制絕育的批評】<br />\n<br />\n橫批：2015-2018短短三年間，喀什和和田的出生率驟降 60%，乃出於「自願」。<br />\n<br />\n//（北京共同社）中國政府智囊團和中國社會科學院旗下的研究機構在9月3日發表報告指，新疆維吾爾自治區的婦女願意接受絕育手術。用來反駁 6月有德國研究人員報告說她們被強制在自治區進行絕育手術。<br />\n<br />\n「計劃生育」是中國的一個重要課題。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，由於「宗教極端主義、恐怖主義和國家分裂主義」的影響，特別在喀什和和田等自治區的南部地區，許多出生是「基於過度計劃或結婚」。 由於加強管理和宣傳，報告聲稱「民眾自己選擇了適合自己的長期避孕措施」，並接受了免費手術。//<br />\n<br />\n新聞報導原文：<a href=\"https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/a4df36ca2981a49720a5c2f129d878e4f8cfee07\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.yahoo.co.jp%2Farticles%2Fa4df36ca2981a49720a5c2f129d878e4f8cfee07&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=e3df20aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/a4df36ca2981a49720a5c2f129d878e4f8cfee07</a>"},{"pid":"50618710952e19adfbd72aee9b38aed877816854","tid":2190552,"uid":15605,"like":205,"dislike":2,"score":203,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:35:01.000Z","msg":"南京人民當年係自殺添呀"},{"pid":"9fb134654813ea561b6db16dcc