://www.facebook.com/knockofftranslation/photos/a.107312867772482/109047527599016/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A78fabn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA78fabn.jpg&h=d097214c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【新疆絕育乃「自願」 中國駁斥德國研究人員對強制絕育的批評】<br />\n<br />\n橫批：2015-2018短短三年間，喀什和和田的出生率驟降 60%，乃出於「自願」。<br />\n<br />\n//（北京共同社）中國政府智囊團和中國社會科學院旗下的研究機構在9月3日發表報告指，新疆維吾爾自治區的婦女願意接受絕育手術。用來反駁 6月有德國研究人員報告說她們被強制在自治區進行絕育手術。<br />\n<br />\n「計劃生育」是中國的一個重要課題。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，由於「宗教極端主義、恐怖主義和國家分裂主義」的影響，特別在喀什和和田等自治區的南部地區，許多出生是「基於過度計劃或結婚」。 由於加強管理和宣傳，報告聲稱「民眾自己選擇了適合自己的長期避孕措施」，並接受了免費手術。//<br />\n<br />\n新聞報導原文：<a href=\"https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/a4df36ca2981a49720a5c2f129d878e4f8cfee07\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.yahoo.co.jp%2Farticles%2Fa4df36ca2981a49720a5c2f129d878e4f8cfee07&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=e3df20aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/a4df36ca2981a49720a5c2f129d878e4f8cfee07</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T22:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8kUr1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8kUr1a.jpg&h=ab2e4fda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d2eb930f67ac116ff253e56a32525c52b9d99ae","tid":2190552,"uid":234089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"37c0b1ba4e43e58658783a3a6c532ad46432bfc4","tid":2190552,"uid":62259,"like":1,"dislike":30,"score":-29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:38:40.000Z","msg":"根據連登仔標準 唔反抗就係奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T22:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8N0QKTz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8N0QKTz.gif&h=3ae5a79c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dcb6000ce16ffc4fe46b3179baa6c74822bd5d61","tid":2190552,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T23:04:46.000Z","msg":"強